    "tagline": "Specializes in real-time rendering, shader development, and optimization with over a decade of self-directed experience in Unity. Check out my work here!",

    "aboutDescription": "<b>My life is built from an unshakable obsession with how digital worlds are made.</b> At six, <em>Super Mario 64</em> was the spark. I grew up with its modding scene, teaching myself <em>Game Maker</em> in 2007, spending late nights modeling levels in <em>SketchUp</em> and resolving emulation bugs. In 2015 came <em>Unity3D</em> and finally shaders, which I've spent a decade mastering. Today, my lifelong devotion translates into building ultra-performant rendering systems and effects — all to give players the same spark I first felt.",

